<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.4.2">
<l>kūvumā ṟaṟiya māṭṭēṉ kuṉṟaṅka ḷaṉaittu meṉkō</l>
<l>mēvucīr māri yeṉkō viḷaṅkutā rakaika ḷeṉkō</l>
<l>nāviyal kalaika ḷeṉkō ñāṉanal lāvi yeṉkō</l>
<l>pāvucīrk kaṇṇa ṉemmāṉ paṅkayak kaṇṇa ṉaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I don’t know the way to call [him]: Will I say “all the hills”?</l>
<l>Will I say “showers of lasting excellence”? Will I say “shining stars”?</l>
<l>Will I say “arts the nature of the tongue”? Will I say “good soul of knowledge”?</l>
<l>– Kṛṣṇa of wide-spread fame, our lord, the one with lotus eyes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
